titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (PHENYLKETONURIA) - Description

div.p: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (PHENYLKETONURIA) is the same as attribute NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS.
NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (PHENYLKETONURIA) is the result of screening for Phenylketonuria (PKU).
